  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chopped onions and garlic, sautéing until they become translucent and fragrant.",
    "Chop challots into thin rounds and add them to the pan. Cook for about 3-5 minutes on each side or until golden brown.",
    "Add bell peppers and tomatoes to the skillet, tossing well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper, adjust seasoning if necessary.",
    "Serve hot as a snack or appetizer."
